{"data": {"node": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7548184711907979", "organization": {"id": "538694416590691", "viewer_permissions": [], "application_groupings": {"nodes": [{"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "7548184711907979"}]}, "id": "435446728865026"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "9584449888295981"}]}, "id": "232370719693323"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "5872942456118694"}]}, "id": "986121008958661"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "6121529404565492"}]}, "id": "703135847908676"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "4949545151733381"}]}, "id": "474916424042047"}]}}, "firstRevision": {"nodes": [{"application": {"id": "7548184711907979", "release_date": 1718550000, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8319843578075418"}, "id": "978246270470209"}]}}, "binary": null, "live_binary": null, "created_date": 1724394739, "id": "8270079573051819", "is_initial_release": false, "name_with_fallback": "v5", "pdp_metadata_with_fallback": {"version": 5, "application": {"is_concept": false, "latest_released_pdp_metadata": {"id": "8293458767380566"}, "release_status": "RELEASED", "id": "7548184711907979"}, "id": "8293458767380566", "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED"}, "release_date": null, "administration_status": "APPROVED", "is_first": false, "release_status": "RELEASED", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "pdp_metadata": {"application": {"default_locale": "en_US", "id": "7548184711907979", "is_first_party": false, "enables_in_app_ads": false, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF"}, "iarc_cert": {"id": "470122712016569"}, "iarc_email": null, "msrp": null, "translations": {"nodes": [{"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "1902743293537470", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "\u00c9vasion de la Chambre \u00c9trange", "keywords": ["Sortie8", "\u00c9vasion", "Horreur", "vroid", "Anime"], "long_description": "Pr\u00e9parez-vous \u00e0 transformer votre pi\u00e8ce en d\u00e9fi d'\u00e9vasion ultime avec \"Odd Room Escape\". Plongez dans cette exp\u00e9rience palpitante de r\u00e9alit\u00e9 mixte qui vous immerge dans un espace rempli de divers objets, poussant vos comp\u00e9tences en m\u00e9moire et observation \u00e0 leur limite. Votre mission : rep\u00e9rer les changements subtils dans l'am\u00e9nagement de la pi\u00e8ce. Chaque identification correcte vous rapproche de la lib\u00e9ration de cet environnement \u00e9trange. Pr\u00e9parez-vous \u00e0 des surprises \u00e9tranges et inattendues dans cette aventure captivante !", "short_description": "Transformez votre espace en un d\u00e9fi d'\u00e9vasion avec \"Odd Room Escape\". Cette aventure en R\u00e9alit\u00e9 Mixte met \u00e0 l'\u00e9preuve votre m\u00e9moire et vos comp\u00e9tences d'observation alors que vous chassez les changements subtils dans votre pi\u00e8ce. Rep\u00e9rez les diff\u00e9rences, d\u00e9couvrez des surprises inqui\u00e9tantes et trouvez votre chemin pour sortir de cet environnement myst\u00e9rieux. Pr\u00e9parez-vous pour une exp\u00e9rience palpitante !"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "cover_2560_1440_us.png", "id": "8180434605336771", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/428854327_8180434612003437_1853515920590945524_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dxfX0v9m-WgQ7kNvgEkFkQV&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBY8iVRjOOhXPlk16FOkyxpiUMaaRUuPIGGe73GGSczTQ&oe=6707C0BF"}, {"file_name": "pdp_3000_900_us.png", "id": "1691461168372047", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.ocul